<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="mount-v">mount <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /maʊnt/    美 /maʊnt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>【正式用语】爬（上）；骑（上）:</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I mounted the steps and looked around me slowly.
我爬上台阶，慢慢环顾四周。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-arrange">2.★ <strong>组织；安排（arrange）</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>mount a protest / an exhibition
发起抗议/举办展览</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>逐步增加</strong></h4></div>